*Smemo* da se pohvalimo svojim uspesima. (We can be proud of our successes.) 

Često *smem* da budem nezavisna. (I often dare to be independent.)

Njegovi roditelji *smeli* da mu pomognu. (His parents dared to help him.)

*Smemo* da tražimo bolji život. (We can demand a better life.) 

Mora da *smemne* da se suprostavi. (She must have the courage to oppose.)